    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Assassinvisible</strong> is a stealth and puzzle game in which your character is invisible -sometimes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207460/extras/77d9fd5191a043daa156bcc3055d812f.avif?t=1734120677\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207460/extras_big/77d9fd5191a043daa156bcc3055d812f.avif?t=1734120677 width=800 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To avoid dying from boredom in class, Camille decides to draw <strong>your</strong> adventures on her notebook. You're an assassin sneaking around each page's squares to reach their target and erase it forever. Analyze the situations, avoid being spotted by the guards and discover the life of the child drawing your stories through their notebook's margins! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn levels (that the kid made, certainly not us) with ever complexifying, unique and intersting situations -absolutly no filler. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original <i>gameplay</i> where the character is invisible for the enemies, but also for the players! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A touching story told through a pupil's notebook. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ultimate <strong>revenge</strong> for all those years spent being bored (and having fun) in class.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207460/extras/e8a42135b9482c5acb4cb5b818a866a2.poster.avif?t=1734120677\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207460/extras/e8a42135b9482c5acb4cb5b818a866a2.webm?t=1734120677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207460/extras/e8a42135b9482c5acb4cb5b818a866a2.mp4?t=1734120677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
